{"article_id":"vDOiYdUqJtZOXUsp","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Even before Christine Blasey Ford accused Supreme Court choice Brett Kavanaugh of sexual assault ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"the nomination was said to be about women .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"Appointing Mr Kavanaugh would tip the court 's balance in favour of Republicans .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"This sparked real fear amongst progressive women","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that landmark Roe v Wade decision","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"that granted the right","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"to abortion","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"could be overturned .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"In 2016 the potential","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"for the first majority conservative line-up on the court in decades","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"brought reluctant Trump voters to the ballot box .","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"Once Mr Kavanaugh denied Ms Ford 's allegations ,","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"the hearings became a test","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"of how far the Me Too movement has changed America .","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"The BBC spoke to women before and after the extraordinary hearing","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"to find out","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"whether this is really about women 's rights .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Did listening to Dr Ford and Mr Kavanaugh change their minds about who and what to believe ?","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"Already suspicious of Mr Kavanaugh 's social values , progressive women 's opposition escalated","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"when sexual assault claims emerged .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Julia Peters , 33 , has been attending protests in Washington DC for a week .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"`` This is n't someone","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"we can elect out .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"He will be in there for a lifetime ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"and we know","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"he does n't stand for our values , ''","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"she said at Capitol Hill","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"before the hearings began .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Grace Perret , a college junior , is from New Orleans , Louisiana , one of the four US states with a `` trigger law ''","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"that mean","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"abortion would be banned automatically","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"if Roe v Wade was overturned .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"`` This would have devastating implications for poor women especially ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"who likely can not afford to travel '' to other states","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"to seek abortions ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"she explained .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"The promise","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"`` we believe women '' is core for Julia :","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"`` We are here","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"to let Christine Blasey Ford know","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"we believe her . ''","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"There is anger at how quickly some on the right dismissed Dr Ford 's allegations ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"which have caused great distress to her family .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"`` The attempts by so many on the right","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"to paint this as a co-ordinated political smear campaign","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"is incredibly damaging to the anti-rape culture movement and to survivors everywhere , ''","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"commented Ms Perret .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"But conservative women are deeply concerned about what they see as an abuse of the confirmation process .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"Rachel Gill , 22 , went to Capitol Hill on Thursday","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"to show her support for Mr Kavanaugh","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"because she believes in the `` principle of innocent until proven guilty '' .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"`` I absolutely do support women","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"who have come forward","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"to talk about these experiences ,","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"but I also think","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"there needs to be proof","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"if you 're going to take someone to court .","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"`` I 'm here","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"because I want to hear the truth ,","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"and if there is any truth to these accusations , ''","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"she explained .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Talk of a smear campaign against Mr Kavanaugh is common","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"as some conservative women fear","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"the assault allegations are being weaponised by Democrats","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"who want to prevent Mr Kavanaugh 's confirmation .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"Nancy Wilson , a grandmother of 11 , travelled to Washington from Fairfax County , Virginia , with two friends .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"Wearing `` I Stand With Brett '' T-shirts ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"they explained","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"they believe","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"women are being misused .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"They want Mr Kavanaugh on the court","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"because he 's a `` constitutionalist judge '' .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"`` The process is being abused .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"It 's become a circus .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"Sex should not be inserted into politics like this .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"Someone came along at the 11th hour with an accusation about something","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"that happened 35 years ago , ''","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"Nancy explained .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"On Thursday the world finally heard from Dr Ford and Mr Kavanaugh , in tearful testimonies","depth":4},{"id":79,"text":"that took strikingly different tones .","depth":4},{"id":80,"text":"# KavanaughHearings trended all day on social media ,","depth":4},{"id":81,"text":"prompting survivors of sexual violence to tell their own stories ,","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"including a 76-year-old woman","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"who called the TV network C-Span about her experience of rape .","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"After protesting outside the Senate ,","depth":4},{"id":85,"text":"Chicago-born Lucy Melchor , 36 , watched the hearings .","depth":4},{"id":86,"text":"`` I thought","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"Ms Ford 's testimony was heartbreaking and compelling .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"It just reinforced that I believe her , ''","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"`` When asked who committed the assault ,","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"she replied","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"without skipping a beat .","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"And I thought ,","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"she is there under oath ,","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"with her family life having been destroyed .","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"What has she got to gain from this ?","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"Her motive seemed pure and clear . ''","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"In contrast , she felt","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"Mr Kavanaugh 's testimony turned the attention away from a woman 's claims of sexual assault to his anger about the political process .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"`` I was really upset by the level of vitriol","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"that he brought to this .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"It took the focus away from her","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"and put it on politics .","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"That was so difficult to see , ''","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"where progressives found Ms Ford powerfully believable ,","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"conservative women felt exactly the same about Mr Kavanaugh .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"`` I think","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"they both believe what they are saying .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"I believe","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"that Ms Ford probably was assaulted but not by Mr Kavanaugh .","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"My heart really does go out to Dr Ford , ''","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"Rachel Gill explained .","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"Kay Lucien , one of the grandmothers","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"who joined rallies on Capitol Hill ,","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"called Mr Kavanaugh 's comments `` compelling '' and `` passionate . ''","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"Like the judge , Mrs Lucien has a strong religious faith .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"`` I found it so moving","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"that Mr Kavanaugh 's child would offer to pray for a woman","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"who has brought so much pain to her family , ''","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"she explained after the hearing .","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"While she feels sympathy for Dr Ford ,","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"she says","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"her confidence in Mr Kavanaugh 's suitability for the court increased .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"`` I would be pleased","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"if the balance of the Supreme Court court changed in favour of conservatives","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"- we 've seen our country slide in the other direction","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"and we would like to move it back a little bit .","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"`` I would worry less about losing some rights , such as religious rights and gun rights and a lot of things","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"that seem to be attacked constantly in recent years , ''","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"she added .","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"The hearings are also a moment of reckoning for women 's rights in America .","depth":5},{"id":134,"text":"Democrat Ms Melchor commented ,","depth":6},{"id":135,"text":"`` It 's now almost a year since the Me Too movement ,","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"and","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"if the cards fall onto the side of not believing her story ,","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"it 's really detrimental for the women","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"who have been assaulted","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"and will be assaulted in the future .","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"It creates fear for them","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"that they wo n't be believed in the future","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"and that 's what upset them the most . ''","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":287,"left":221,"right":286,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":221,"left":157,"right":220,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":154,"right":156,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":154,"left":151,"right":153,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":145,"right":150,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":2,"right":149,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":149,"left":3,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":147,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":147,"left":4,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":152,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":152,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":11,"right":155,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":155,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":203,"right":219,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":160,"right":202,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":160,"left":159,"right":17,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":159,"left":14,"right":158,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"